reviews.review_text: Kansas Dead on July 4! Appreciate all the work that went into this Matrix recording!  (Using different sources, pasting into channels, etc.)  Very enjoyable show to listen to!  Thanks!!  Nice transition from "Space" into "The Wheel".  Stellar Stella!
